name: Volrath's Laboratory
originalText:
As Volrath's Laboratory enters the battlefield, choose a color and a creature type.
{5}, {T}: Put a 2/2 creature token of the chosen color and type onto the battlefield.

rulings.text: The token does not have any built-in abilities. For example, choosing creature type Bird does not give the token Flying.
The token has the same name as the creature type.
